Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(300,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Shine! The Sage's Jewel"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, let's go rest over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's probably just\N another ridiculous trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the day when me and Mokuba were adopted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every object is composed of atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An atom is composed of the atomic nucleus and electrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you have been adopted by the Kaiba's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you catch up with Gozaburo-{\i1}sama{\i0}, there will be no time for you to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you and Mokuba-sama change your minds and want to leave this place now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... what are your visions for the future of Kaiba Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do when you inherit Kaiba Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to... build Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaiba Land"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother wants to build a game paradise for underprivileged kids like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Game paradise", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ridiculous!\N It's too boring for words!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me\N this is your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Games are not boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Games purify our souls and leave room for new development that challenges the mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the products of human wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"S-So what"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they make the world turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I want you to inherit Kaiba Corporation is so you become a ruthless dictator of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... confiscate all of their toys and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you learn what it means to {\i1}be{\i0} that ruthless dictator,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you touch games or toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that after gathering all the toys and games in you guys' luggage, there's almost nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class will begin shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way my brother is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What might the problem be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Please...\N Give this to my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot to\N take his reference book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are starting in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother... please don't let them steal our most important treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use these cards to help you relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all trashy cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, I'll get the {\i1}real{\i0} one some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some outstanding brotherly love you two have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... You sure had it hard early on in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you showing us all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to refresh your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to remember what you did to Gozaburo Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later,\N {\i1}judgment{\i0} will come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, just who the hell {\i1}are{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eagerly {\i1}waiting{\i0}\N for that time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although we've been moving forward in this darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we seem to have forgotten about one important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a {\b0}game{\b1} we're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as we have a stronger Monster Card than the one guarding the door, the doors will keep opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the first most important rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First most important rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! If we wanna get out of this maze, there should be a {\i1}second{\i0} rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}did{\i0} think it was a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In each room we enter, there's a set of doors with the Level Stars ranging from one to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right... that guides us on how to get out of this endless loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We just went through a One Star door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go through the Two Star door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold. Please save me, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, no matter how loud you cry for your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're the only ones in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I used Offerings for the Dead last turn, I can't draw during this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have one card in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry and send out a Monster, my cute Flying Penguin is going to attack you directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Call me to the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Deck Master can be played as a Special Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You don't have enough Attack Power to beat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Deck Master is defeated, the player will lose the game instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without Black Magician, Black Magician Girl's partner, she's nothing but a little cosplay-girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need your strength later on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No {\i1}way{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Summon a Monster in Defense Mode and end this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you don't have any Wall Monsters in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Flying Penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penguin Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, just a weak little angel, was it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Helping Angel's Effect, I get to pick one card from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can tell this turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu Mazaki, 16 years old, the card you picked is the only one you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your life-saving chain is only a useless magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no other way to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you out\N by {\i1}using your body{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd let someone like {\i1}you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to bet\N everything on this draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please lend me your strength, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Attack Power, 1550?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't defeat his Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait... Maha Vailo is a strong magician with a hidden ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden ability...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which card is the most like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm... since you have so many cards, there must be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it's Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd {\b0}like{\b1} to say that, but he fits my other self better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maha Vailo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... this may not be the best Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it doesn't really have the strongest Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it has a hidden ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can use this power at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maha Vailo's hidden ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! I'll Summon Maha Vailo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I'll use a Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip it with Magician's Spell Book!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity that my Flying Penguin has 2200 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're still a bit inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Maha Vailo has a hidden ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When equipped with an Equipment Card, it receives a 500 point power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maha Vailo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Yu-Gi-Oh Episode 103 Subbed'' originally Encoded by Nealhon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks Kamesennin2 for helping him with the subtitles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was Anzu's voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When she calls my name, Anzu doesn't really want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one she's {\b0}really{\b1} calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know very well who she wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Level Three Star door?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Do it, Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Holy Barrier - Mirror Force... exactly what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at the top of the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that covered card there a reverse card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... how about {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Berfomet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, this is the last door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are five set cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get this far, we've used a lot of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you waste the few cards we have left,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we may not get out of this labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are only five cards left in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Four Star Monster\N and five covered cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! He's our last trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll use this! Heavy Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good, the covered cards are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Four Star Ladybug of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Four Star Ladybug of Death is a card with the Effect to destroy Level Four Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu! Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was too careless to look down upon you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll make you regret what you just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play Volt Penguin in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also play a reverse card to end this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I doubt there are many Monsters that have an Attack Power over 2550.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'd better finish this fast just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Maha Vailo to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Lightning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chance is soon at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant Magic, activate!!\N Revenge Sacrifice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maha Vailo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge Sacrifice can destroy the\NMonster and present it as a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll Summon a new Monster to take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summoned Guardian of Ice - Defender Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2450 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you overpower this Monster and attack me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I Summon Penguin Torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of my Deck Master, it gets a power-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Penguin Torpedo can attack the player directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're at your limit!\N Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I can't attack, the opponent won't be able to attack very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally came out to play, ya piece of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it gets destroyed then I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, activate!\N Ocean of Regeneration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is able to revive a Water-Attribute Monster from the Graveyard for one turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, the 16-year-old Anzu Mazaki's life is like a fading candle flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu... Anzu's gonna be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't help at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... I believe in the power of Black Magician Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There should be one card that can save us in your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't pick that card for my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't choose Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the first card that you picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Sage's Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right... that is the card that will grant us a miracle and give me the power to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, it'd be too coincidental to draw that card during my next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time I activated\N my Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sleeping comrades...\N please lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magic Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Circle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master Ability borrows the power of our comrades sleeping in the Graveyard and draws five cards from your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 16-year-old Anzu Mazaki doesn't {\i1}have{\i0} that card in her deck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm on the field and The Sage's Jewel is played, I can call my master, Black Magician for one turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WH-WHAT'D YOU SAY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! I was so close to getting a new, young and sexy body~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu... you're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should say it was... {\i1}refreshing entertainment{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow got away from that old, perverted penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to reunite with Yugi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder what\N happened to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's started his Duel already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing Deck Master is Judge Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Duel is a... "Trial Duel"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dangerous foe to deal with!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deck Master: Judge Man's Judgment"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:23:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
